==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Spineless
<hw>Spine"less</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Having
no spine, or vertebral column.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Having no thorns or barbs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>lacking in strength of character; cowardly, in a
physical or moral sense.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Spinescence</ent>⟦br⟧
